excerpt from a story i'll never write
body:
l o v e

God, I’m in love with this girl.

It just hit me, out of nowhere.

She wasn’t doing anything different, wearing anything special.

She didn’t have to.

She was just sitting there, wearing the sweatshirt she stole from me and the old pyjama pants, her hair in a mess, her face void of any make up, her favourite book in her hand.

That’s all she did, be herself.

That’s all she had to do to make me fall for her.

And, man, did I fall.

I fell for the way she sleeps, hogging most of the bed.

The way she complains about her weight but is too lazy to work out.

The way she loves watching horror movies but gets scared while watching them.

The way she laughs.

The way she talks.

The way she is.

Her insecurities.

Her quirks.

Her flaws.

I fell in love with all of her.

And I don’t mind that.

~~~~~

A/n: Jfc I don’t know what that was. It was just in my head and I had to post it somewhere so I posted it here. It’s my first time posting my writing here so please be kind in your criticism. And I’m so sorry for the length.

blog.description:
masterlist: https://harrystxleslx.tumblr.com/post/179214111135/masterlist
REQUESTS ARE OPEN!
Prompt List: https://harrystxleslx.tumblr.com/post/179241418460/prompts

body:
Prompts!

Request away!

3. “Hey, hey, calm down. They can’t hurt you anymore.”

4. “I’m not here to make friends.”

5. “Well, that’s tragic.”

6. “You can’t banish me! This is my bed too!”

7. “I need a place to stay.”

8. “Good thing I didn’t ask for your opinion.”

9. “What’s the matter, sweetie?”

10. “Did you just hiss at me?”

11. “Did you just hiss at me?”

12. “Take your medicine.”

13. “I feel like I can’t breathe.”

14. “You need to see a doctor.”

15. “I was a joke, baby. I swear.”

16. “I didn’t think you could get any less romantic…”

17. “They’re not your kids, back the f*ck off.”

18. “I’m late.”

19. “Just get home as soon as possible, okay?!”

20. “Are you going to talk to me?”

21. “We need to talk.”

22. “I want a pet.”

23. “Just smile, I really need to see you smile right now.”

24. “Does he know about the baby?“

25. “Don’t argue. Just do it.”

26. “Show me what’s behind your back.”

27. “STOP INTERRUPTING ME!”

28. “Tell me you need me.”

29. “I had a bad dream again.”

30. “It’s Christmas, don’t be mad at me.”

31. “I know we aren’t really talking right now but please, call me back. It’s important.”

32. “Why are you still here?”

33. “I didn’t come here to talk to you. Where is he?”

34. “I’m sorry, I wasn’t thinking.” “Are you ever?”

35. “You were sitting alone, I thought I’d keep you company.”

36. “I like your outfit…never mind, it’s our uniform…sorry, I’m bad at this.”

37. “Can you stop being dramatic and call them?”

38. “I haven’t loved anyone or anything as much as I love this dog.”

39. “I would fist fight a tornado for you.”

40. “You can’t just be normal for one day, can you?”

41. “Goddammit! I hate you! I hate you and your dumb voice and your stupid muscles and your awfully attractive face!”

42. “You know, I used to dream about ending your life, now I dream about spending it by your side.”

43. “You know what they say, Love and Hate are two sides of a very, very thin line…”

A/N

Please request! I’d be happy to write them!
